{"type":null,"faqId":37065,"title":"如何连接两部手机？（更换手机如何连接手环？）","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 0.9111111in 1.25in 1.0in 1.25in;}\n.p1{text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:宋体;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span>手环连接手机</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>1、手环与第一部手机通过蓝牙正常连接。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>2、长按手环侧按键，当手环上蓝牙图标闪烁时，点击第二部手机蓝牙列表中的“HUAWEI B2-XXX”，连接第二部手机。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>说明：</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>此时手环与第一部手机的蓝牙连接会自动断开。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>3、再次点击第一部手机蓝牙列表中的“HUAWEI B2-XXX”进行连接。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>当手环主界面显示</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=121727\" style=\"width:0.2361111in;height:0.2361111in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>时，表明手环已成功连接两部手机。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":212,"faqType":"其他","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"2229","faqTypeCode":"Wearable_Device-Others","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1440750141000,"seriesProductName":"B2","visitedTimes":69,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"华为手环,B2,连接两部手机,更换手机连接,数据同步,同系统连接","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}